Section : Preparation (20) Attachment :
Workloading : (Min) LeadingTime : (Min) Phase :
Note: This case need cover all CPU & GPU & RAM types.
1. Flash the latest BIOS.

2. Preload the latest images(CN) and OOBE.
3. Check the device manager and ensure no yellow hang exist

4. Check the related app verison in the machine

PCM version should ≥ 5.1.70.6273


百应 version should ≥ 2.4.0.0 (Only for SMB)


Lenovo store version should ≥ 9.0.1530.0515 (Only for x86)
 
Section : Voice Conversation (20) Attachment :
Workloading : (Min) LeadingTime : (Min) Phase :

1. Click microphone button and say below content and send it. CN: 帮我生成一个10天的上海旅行计划

天禧智能体 can generate the result with audio playback.

2. Mute the Voice broadcast in 天禧智能体's setting and and say below content and send it. CN: 帮我生成一个7天的北京旅行计划

Ensure 天禧智能体 can generate the result smoothly but not boardcast the answer

3. Unmute the Voice broadcast in 天禧智能体's setting，modify system volumn by hotkey when answer play back

Ensure the voice play back without error
4. Mute system volumn by hotkey and make a voice conversation
Ensure the conversation can generate successfully
5. Volumn increase by hotkey when answer play back
Ensure the answer can play back smoothly
 
Section : AI Space (40) Attachment :
Workloading : (Min) LeadingTime : (Min) Phase :
AI space

Click the AI Space button at the bottom of left sidebar and click the "发现更多" button.

Ensure AI Space page can be opened.

Click the below applets: AI PPT, AI画师 (If preload without Creator Zone, please skip AI画师 part)

Ensure the applets can be opened.

Quickly click the square expand button at the top left corner of the main window to open and close the expanded window 10 times.

Make sure the UI doesn't get lag or crash.
Try rotating, erecting, disassembling or expanding the screen when the machine supports these features. (Such as Dual screen,Multimode Display)
Make sure the expandable window on the left side of the main page still works in a variety of screen modes.

Section : High Talk mode (60) Attachment :
Workloading : (Min) LeadingTime : (Min) Phase :
High Talk mode

Click the AI Space button and click "发现更多". Search "嗨聊模式" and click the "嗨聊模式" button to open high & talk. (The smartkey can also enter call mode assuming you've set it up in settings.)

Make sure the high talk mode screen can be opened.

Speak to the microphone while 天禧智能体 listening.

Make sure 天禧智能体 can hear and respond to the voice normally.

When 天禧智能体 is replying, click the pause button.

Ensure that the conversation can be paused and resumed.

When 天禧智能体 is replying, click the stop button.

Ensure that the session is successfully terminated and the listening restarts.

When 天禧智能体 is replying, plug in the headset.

Notification of device change pops up, click continue and ensure that it can be conversed.

When 天禧智能体 is listening, plug out the headset.

Notification of device change pops up, click continue and ensure that it can be conversed.
Change the voice speed by click 语速 button: 1. Slow down: 0.8x 2. Faster: 1.2x
Ensure successful application of voice speed setting to next broadcast after changing speed.
Click the 更换声音 button in the lower right coner.
Make sure the sound settings UI is successfully accessed.
Click 克隆我的声音 to clone the voice.
Make sure the clone sound UI is successfully accessed.

Turn off the microphone and then try to talk while 天禧智能体 is listening.

Make sure 天禧智能体 can't hear anything.

Mute the computer speaker when 天禧智能体 is talking.

Make sure the voice broadcast is successfully muted.
Click on the red phone icon to try to end the conversation.
Ensure that the session is successfully terminated and the UI is closed
Stress

Place at least two laptops face to face (Cover DIS and UMA)


1. Enable the high & talk mode


2. The speaking speed is set to 0.8x and 1.2x respectively


3. The voice is set to a man and a woman respectively


4. Try to get two computers to start a conversation using any question

Ensure that the conversation can be successfully at least 60 minutes without black screen, BSOD and crash.

Section : Compatibility Test (80) Attachment :
Workloading : (Min) LeadingTime : (Min) Phase :

If the system without Creator Zone or AI artist, instructions to generate images will be recognized as KB(知识库) summary.

Generation and execute below step1-10 in both AC&DC mode

Access PKB and test with document summary.
1. Modify power mode to default mode
Ensure power mode can modify successfully
2. Download and install below 3rd party applications: QQ Music, Bilibili, Jianying Pro

3. Press SmartKey to launch 天禧智能体 application

Ensure 天禧智能体 can launch without error
4. Launch Edge and open 5 webpages, do some browsing actions
Ensure Edge webpage can launch and browsing without lag
5. Launch QQ music and play an online music (Note: Edge in background)
Ensure QQ music can play without lag
6. Pause QQ music and minimized the window, lauch Bilibili and play an online video
Ensure Bilibili online video can play without lag

7. Upload "西游记介绍.docx" into XiaoTian PKB then do summary with "西游记介绍.docx". 

Ensure 天禧智能体 will generate the result without lag and error
8. Pause Bilibili online video and minimized the window, launch Jianying Pro
Ensure Jianying pro can lauch without lag

9.(If preload with Creator Zone, do this step)


Enter the provided content to generate an image:


CN:帮我画上海东方明珠塔


For version ≥4202, use the AI画师 in the expandable window.


For version ≤4081, use the main window dialog box.

Ensure 天禧智能体 will generate the picture without lag and error

(If preload without Creator Zone, do this step)


Open XiaoTian PKB and do summary with "西游记介绍.docx". 

Ensure 天禧智能体 will generate the result without lag and error
10. Press Alt+Tab button to switch all applications for 10 times
Ensure the application can switch successfully without lag
DC RSOC<20% repeat step 1-10
Ensure without lag or error
 
Section : Power Management (120) Attachment :
Workloading : (Min) LeadingTime : (Min) Phase :

If the system without Creator Zone or AI artist, instructions to generate images will be recognized as KB(知识库) summary.

1. Press SmartKey to launch 天禧智能体, minimized window and it should be running in background.

Access PKB and test with document summary.

2. Do PKB summary with "西游记介绍.docx" and put system into MS/S3 for 3 mins. 

System can enter into MS/S3 without error.

3. Resume from MS/S3 and check the coversation function of 天禧智能体.

After resume 天禧智能体 showed "响应超时，请稍后重试" is accepted but should verify XiaoTian can successfully do document summary again .

4. Repeat step 2-3 5 times

天禧智能体 works normally.

5.(If preload with Creator Zone, do this step)


Enter the provided content to generate an image and then let system enter S4 for 1 minute. CN: 帮我画联想大厦

System can enter into S4 without error.

(If preload without Creator Zone, do this step)


Do PKB summary with "西游记介绍.docx" and then let system enter S4 for 1 minute. 

System can enter into S4 without error.

6.(If preload with Creator Zone, do this step)


Resume from S4 and verify the generated function with the AI画师 of 天禧智能体.

天禧智能体 could successfully initiate a new generation after resume.

(If preload without Creator Zone, do this step)


Resume from S4 and verify the generated function with the PKB of 天禧智能体.

After resume 天禧智能体 showed "响应超时，请稍后重试" is accepted but should verify XiaoTian can successfully do document summary again .

7. Repeat step 5-6 5 times

天禧智能体 works normally.
8. Put system to CB
System can enter into CB without error.

9. Press power button and login to system, press SmartKey to launch 天禧智能体

天禧智能体 can launch successfully

10. Attach 测试设备.txt to the dialog box and click Summary

Ensure 天禧智能体 can generate a result

11. Repeat step 8-10 5 times

天禧智能体 works normally.

Note: Install Hwinfo and capture the log, please set the polling cycle 1000ms Send the log to wuhf2@lenovo.com, changxd2@lenovo.com

12. Keep 天禧智能体 UI in the foreground and idle for 30 mins

13. Resume to system, enter 天禧智能体 KB and do summary with "西游记介绍.docx". 

Ensure that 天禧智能体 can do document summary successfully.

14. Click x to close 天禧智能体 and idle for 10 mins

Ensure 天禧智能体 list in system tray in lower right corner

15. Launch 天禧智能体 in system tray

Ensure 天禧智能体 will launch successfully in foreground

16. Enter 天禧智能体 KB and do summary with "西游记介绍.docx".

Ensure that 天禧智能体 can do document summary successfully.

17. Uninstall Creator Zone or AI画师 and restart the system.


(If preload without Creator Zone, please skip this step)

Ensure that Creator Zone or AI画师 can be successfully removed
